      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tip-stp-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Tipi stampante da stampare :"
